title: Butt Plug Thursday
description:
Lauren & Jeremy reveal their favorite porn stars. Lauren presses Jeremy on whether or not it’s okay for guys to watch porn while in a relationship. Jeremy explains why he thinks twice before liking a girl’s photo on Instagram.
